匱乏的自由&rdquo;、&ldquo;免於恐懼的自由&rdquo;）。它將保證國家的獨立、團結、統一及與各民主強國的合作。（中央文獻研究室編：《毛澤東文集》第四卷，人民出版社，1996年，第27、28頁）。"},{"pid":"26554b50bab073d857343c8f38343e2eeec34574","tid":1531871,"uid":116526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:05:16.000Z","msg":"天滅中共"},{"pid":"99f565da54ba8e13018825284be4139c9e2399f9","tid":1531871,"uid":98731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:06:33.000Z","msg":"【美國巴絲】請聯絡你嘅地區同州嘅國會代表／議員<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dNDHwS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dNDHwS</a>"},{"pid":"eb614b9a41f82c2a3d8c0e339b556b2324320aa5","tid":1531871,"uid":75277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aeca671ec13c76243d9c67fbada5a376bfd6e2a","tid":1531871,"uid":75277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbde2217417ae751fbb6ec9f377a1d136a59528","tid":1531871,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:43:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91ebf18b0e6c26acbe751d7093194ae68a1cf6e5","tid":1531871,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:44:17.000Z","msg":"國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},{"pid":"7ed74406e54f33631321f79ee70820c2da457000","tid":1531871,"uid":34263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:44:35.000Z","msg":"天滅中共 全黨死清光"},{"pid":"cb45c9095896c030a81d2fd799e1824209c8d3c2","tid":1531871,"uid":75277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:45:48